1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 2 MRSA ยง2, as amended by PL 2023, c. 488, ยง2, is further amended to read:
3 ยง2. Expense account
4 The "Governor's Expense Account" expense account must be credited with $40,000
5 $30,000 annually. This appropriation must be available for expenditure by the Governor at
6 the Governor's discretion. This account is not subject to audit, except as to total amount to
7 be paid. The Governor, on a quarterly basis, shall provide an accounting of expenses made
8 from the Governor's expense account and post that accounting on the Governor's publicly
9 accessible website.
10 SUMMARY
1111 This bill reduces the annual appropriation to the Governor's expense account to
1122 $30,000 and requires the Governor to provide a quarterly accounting of expenses made
1133 from the account and post that accounting on the Governor's publicly accessible website.
